hspell
-------------------------------------------
The Hspell project is a free Hebrew linguistic project.
Its primary goal is to create a free Hebrew spell-checker. 

T he secondary goal is to make the algorithms and dictionaries, created 
initially for the spell-checker, freely available. These could be used 
in more sophisticated research or applications that require Hebrew word 
lists or a Hebrew morphology engine. 

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.21-1
  perl-5.8.7-5
  zlib-1.2.3-1

Build requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.21-1
  autoconf2.5-2.59-2
  binutils-20060709-1
  cygport-0.2.5-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-1
  libtool1.5-1.5.22-1
  make-3.80-1
  gzip-1.3.5-1
  perl-5.8.7-5
  zlib-1.2.3-1

Canonical homepage:
  http://ivrix.org.il/projects/spell-checker/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack hspell-1.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./hspell-1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/hspell-1.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/hspell-1.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libhspell-devel-1.0-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libhspell1-1.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary packages:

(hspell)
  /usr/bin/hspell-i
  /usr/bin/hspell.exe
  /usr/bin/multispell
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/hspell-1.0.README
  /usr/share/doc/hspell-1.0/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/hspell-1.0/INSTALL
  /usr/share/doc/hspell-1.0/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/hspell-1.0/README
  /usr/share/doc/hspell-1.0/TODO
  /usr/share/doc/hspell-1.0/WHATSNEW
  /usr/share/man/man1/hspell.1.gz

(libhspell1)
  /usr/bin/cyghspell-1.dll
  /usr/share/hspell/hebrew.wgz
  /usr/share/hspell/hebrew.wgz.desc
  /usr/share/hspell/hebrew.wgz.hints
  /usr/share/hspell/hebrew.wgz.prefixes
  /usr/share/hspell/hebrew.wgz.sizes
  /usr/share/hspell/hebrew.wgz.stems

(libhspell-devel)
  /usr/include/hspell.h
  /usr/include/linginfo.h
  /usr/lib/libhspell.a
  /usr/lib/libhspell.dll.a
  /usr/lib/libhspell.la
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/hspell.pc
  /usr/share/man/man3/hspell.3.gz

