Port Notes:

----- version 1.0-2 -----
Patched to create a shared library with libtool, as well as provide
a pkg-config file and fix building where builddir != srcdir.
See:  http://www.ivrix.org.il/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=4

----- version 1.0-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 0.9-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 0.8-1 -----
New upstream release.  Includes major changes including a dependency on 
zlib, many new words, and more.  See WHATSNEW for details.

----- version 0.7-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


Cygwin port maintained by:
